item.title: CVE-2023-0146|2024-08-02T05:02:43.795Z -- unknown -- naver%20map
item.description: The Naver Map WordPress plugin through 1.1.0 does not validate and escape some of its shortcode attributes before outputting them back in a page/post where the shortcode is embed, which could allow users with the contributor role and above to perform Stored Cross-Site Scripting attacks.
